{"tid":990392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【勵害了】華為手機疑自動刪除用戶 Twitter 下載圖片　台灣網民都中招","createTime":"2019-01-21T14:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T14:40:23.000Z","uid":28970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac570ef10c5d0b9216d2c5782223b725896738a7","tid":990392,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:09:36.000Z","msg":"用戶擔心華為手機的個人資訊安全問題，事有湊巧，近日有網民嘗試儲存 Twitter（大陸被禁的服務）的圖片時，卻發現下載的圖片遭到「系統服務」自動刪除，用戶聲稱這個圖片被華為手機刪除了。而事情爆發後不久，有台灣網民都發出帖文表示自己都中招，在一部華為榮耀Note 10作測試，在存檔Twitter圖片後，馬上跳出被刪除的訊息。到底是哪方面出問題呢？<br />\n<br />\n繼日前大陸網民 @yxw860510（目前該帳戶已被刪除）報告儲存一張在 Twitter 找到的柴犬圖片，但在儲存後馬上被「系統服務」刪除後，再有台灣網民「discoby」在前日報告，在一部華為榮耀 Note 10 儲存一張 Twitter 圖片，馬上彈出圖片被刪除的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n該網民估計「應該單純是華為的系統軟件」所作出的操作。但亦有網民指這或許是華為軟件的 Bug 令人誤以為華為故意刪除。有網民表示「你的手機軟體一定有後門」「OS不論那一種都有後門，重點是後門拿來做甚麼」「寧願給美國裝間諜軟體」。有台灣網民則擔心，他剛剛才訂了 HUAWEI Mate20 X，不知道該怎麼辦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0v4dD5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0v4dD5.png&h=1902da25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有網民「kanchiam」回應稱懷疑網民「discoby」的手機軟件有後門（圖片來源：mobile01）<br />\n然而帖內另有網民「3cchen」則特地拿中國大陸版華為手機下載 Twitter 圖檔，在 10 分鐘內仍然未被刪除。到底這是個別手機型號出現問題，還是個別地區手機出現問題，且看後續發展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLFWPcE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLFWPcE.png&h=c974a887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/01/21/huaweitwitter/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F01%2F21%2Fhuaweitwitter%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=1L79tNmClEUrvu3H0gBFjNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=4816e660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/01/21/huaweitwitter/tech-secure/</a>"},{"pid":"cc460aae2bdd310ea8e492e4e2b42ae817e8f87a","tid":990392,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e2bdf1998c8ddcde01d38f3cf5ccd0a9d72b2f","tid":990392,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3eac6d0ea37742c4e36a3e600bd6d375e2e80a","tid":990392,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3be7de7ec0a16546397abaff743cb2944259900","tid":990392,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db863c6a6ec67939a18f8aed84c91f5802900bef","tid":990392,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11f69681ec53ca280ecfb6af7b13d68b5b01ef65","tid":990392,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db863c6a6ec67939a18f8aed84c91f5802900bef","tid":990392,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"梳囉屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}